# Sections C, D & E – Documentation, Verification & Clarifying Questions
## AI-Based ECD Decision Support Layer for India

---

# Section C – Documentation Repository Structure

The following structure should be maintained in version control (Git). All documentation is treated as code – reviewed, versioned, and tagged alongside software releases.

```
/docs
├── 00_overview
│   ├── README.md                         # System overview and navigation guide
│   ├── glossary.md                       # Domain + technical term definitions
│   └── stakeholder_map.md                # Roles, responsibilities, contact matrix
│
├── 01_architecture
