│   ├── data_flow_diagram.md              # Primary + secondary + governance flows
│   ├── api_structure.md                  # API endpoint catalogue (auto-generated from OpenAPI)
│   ├── database_schema.md                # Full ER diagram + schema definitions
│   ├── offline_sync_protocol.md          # Sync queue, conflict resolution specification
│   └── infrastructure_config.md          # Server topology, K8s config, NIC cloud setup
│
├── 02_api
