### Documentation Standards
- All markdown documents reviewed via pull request before merge
- OpenAPI spec auto-generated from FastAPI annotations; manually reviewed quarterly
- Model Card and Bias Report updated with every model version release
- Audit Log Specification is immutable once approved; changes require government sign-off
- Field Training Manuals produced in English + regional language (state-specific)

